  [2]: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/AJAX/Getting_Started
  [3]: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API/Writing_WebSocket_client_applications
  [4]: https://pugjs.org
  [5]: https://expressjs.com/pt-br/guide/using-template-engines.html

