doReturn(...).when(spy).exchange(...)
```

The obvious solution would be to inject the `RestTemplate` instead of instantiating one locally but as you said that you can not change the existing code I would suggest to use [PowerMock with Mockito][1] to replace the constructor call of the `RestTemplate` using the [`PowerMockito.whenNew`][2] method.

